messages.message:
Hi Team*,*
We noticed that stats data after 4th June is currently missing across all SaaS stacks in VictoriaMetrics. At this point, data beyond that date won't be visible.
While we have backups in place, we're prioritizing root cause investigation by attempting to reproduce the issue in a single stack before initiating any restoration steps.
Tracking this through following incident: <#C0903PA43V0|>
